data.name: chooseFolder
data.value: Choose a folder to convert to an iFolder.

data.name: ifolderlimiterror
data.value: iFolder could not be created as you are exceeding the limit of ifolders set by your Administrator.

data.name: iFolderCreateError
data.value: An error was encountered while creating the iFolder.

data.name: createPrompt
data.value: The specified location does not exist. Do you want to create it?

data.name: accessDenied
data.value: You do not have sufficient access to the selected location. iFolders can only be created in folders where you have access to read and write files. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: createAccount
data.value: To begin using iFolder, you must first set up an iFolder account. Would you like to set up an iFolder account now?

data.name: invalidCharsError
data.value: The selected location contains invalid characters. The characters \:*?"<>| cannot be used in an iFolder. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: pathInStoreError
data.value: The selected location is inside the iFolder data folder. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: pathContainsStoreError
data.value: The selected location contains the iFolder data files. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: systemDirError
data.value: The selected location contains a system folder. System folders cannot contain an iFolder. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: systemDriveError
data.value: The selected location is a system drive. System drives cannot contain an iFolder. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: winDirError
data.value: The selected location includes the Windows folder. The Windows folder cannot contain an iFolder. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: progFilesDirError
data.value: The selected location includes the Program Files folder. The Program Files folder cannot contain an iFolder. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: containsiFolderError
data.value: The selected location already contains an iFolder. iFolders cannot exist inside other iFolders. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: pathIniFolderError
data.value: The selected location is inside another iFolder. iFolders cannot exist inside other iFolders. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: rootDriveError
data.value: iFolders cannot exist at the drive level. The location selected is at the root of the drive. Please select a location that is not at the root of a drive and try again.

data.name: networkPathError
data.value: The selected location is on a network or non-physical drive. iFolders must reside on a physical drive. Please select a different location and try again.

data.name: PPSDontMatch
data.value: Passphrase and re-typed passphrase doesn't match

data.name: PPForEncryption
data.value: Passphrase should be supplied for encrypting the iFolder

data.name: LoginToDomain
data.value: You have to be logged-in to the domain for creating an encrypted iFolder.

data.name: verifyCert
data.value: iFolder cannot verify the identity of the iFolder Server {0}. The certificate for this iFolder Server was signed by an unknown certifying authority. You might be connecting to a server that is pretending to be {0} which could put your confidential information at risk. Before accepting this certificate, you should check with your system administrator. Do you want to accept this certificate permanently and continue to connect?

data.name: NoCertWarning
data.value: There is no Recovery Agent selected. Encrypted data cannot be recovered later, if passphrase is lost. Do you want to continue?
